RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT REASON_CODE, REASON_DESC FROM OLTMS_REASON WHERE MODULE_CODE ='OL' AND EVENT_CODE = 'VAMB' AND AUTH_STAT ='A' AND RECORD_STAT ='O' ORDER BY REASON_CODE
SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT WHERE BRANCH = NVL(?,GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH) AND MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A') ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO

SELECT COMPONENT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_DFLT_SCHEDULES WHERE PRODUCT = ? UNION SELECT 'INSTALMENT' FROM OLTM_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND ALLOW_INSTALMENT = 'Y' UNION SELECT COMPONENT FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTB_CONTRACT CS, OLTB_CONTRACT_MASTER LD WHERE CS.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LD.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CS.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CS.LATEST_VERSION_NO = LD.VERSION_NO AND NVL(LD.AGENCY_CONTRACT, 'N') = 'Y') UNION SELECT CF.COMPONENT FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE CF, LFTM_PRODUCT_FEE FE, OLTB_CONTRACT CS, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER LD WHERE CF.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CF.CONTRACT_REF_NO = CS.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CF.EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(CF1.EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE CF1 WHERE CF.CONTRACT_REF_NO = CF1.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CF.COMPONENT = CF1.COMPONENT) AND FE.COMPONENT = CF.COMPONENT AND LD.CONTRACT_REF_NO = CS.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CS.LATEST_VERSION_NO = LD.VERSION_NO AND sypks_utils.get_product(CF.CONTRACT_REF_NO) = FE.PRODUCT_CODE AND NVL(LD.AGENCY_CONTRACT, 'N') = 'N' AND FE. BASIS_AMOUNT_TAG <> 'USERINPUT' UNION SELECT component FROM lftms_product_iccf WHERE product = ? AND basis_amount_category = 'D' MINUS SELECT 'PRINCIPAL' FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND VERSION_NO = ? AND NVL(ROLLING_LOAN, 'N') = 'Y' AND MATURITY_TYPE = 'C' MINUS SELECT COMPONENT FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND NVL(RETAIN_MAIN_COMP_PROP, 'N') = 'Y'
SELECT distinct A.counterparty,A.customer_name1 FROM OLVWS_VAMI_SUMMARY A WHERE A.auth_status = 'A' AND A.contract_status = 'A' ORDER BY A.counterparty
SELECT REASON_CODE, REASON_DESC FROM OLTM_REASON WHERE MODULE_CODE='OL' AND EVENT_CODE='REVC' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY 1

SELECT brn_code, brn_name, eoti_desc, time_level FROM (SELECT a.branch_code brn_code,a.branch_name brn_name, decode(b.end_of_input, 'N', 'Transaction Input', 'T','End of Transaction Input', 'F', 'End Of Financial Input', 'E','End of Day','B', 'Beginning of Day') eoti_desc,b.time_level time_level FROM sttm_core_branch a, sttm_core_branch_status b WHERE a.branch_code = b.branch_code and a.auth_stat = 'A' AND a.record_stat = 'O' AND a.branch_code IN (select branch_code from smvw_user_branches u where u.user_id = global.user_id) AND a.branch_code IN (select branch_code from smvw_consolidated_userrole r where r.user_id = global.user_id /*AND r.branch_code<> global.current_branch*/)) WHERE 1 = 1
